    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly & Honest \u2014 Great Opportunity for the Right Buyer! \ud83d\udd27 This vehicle is in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with you! The good news? It does run, giving you a solid foundation to work with. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including dents and scratches, and the interior reflects its age and use. It will need meaningful repairs and attention before it's road-ready for daily driving. If you're a hands-on buyer, a DIY mechanic, or someone looking for an affordable project, this could be exactly what you're searching for \u2014 priced honestly to reflect its current state. Come take a look and see the potential! \ud83d\udd27",
      "price": 5500.0,
