      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, dependable ride without breaking the bank? This vehicle is a great option for budget-conscious buyers who want reliable transportation! It shows the expected signs of everyday use \u2014 some wear on the interior and a few cosmetic imperfections on the exterior \u2014 but it runs well and is ready to get you where you need to go. Nothing flashy, but honest and functional \u2014 a practical choice for the savvy shopper!",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and represents a reliable, well-maintained used car purchase. The exterior presents nicely with only minor surface blemishes \u2014 light scuffs and small scratches consistent with normal everyday use \u2014 but no significant dents, rust, or structural damage. The paint retains good color and gloss overall. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing moderate wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but free of major stains, tears, or damage. All primary features and controls function as expected. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and starts without hesitation; routine maintenance has been kept reasonably up to date. The tires have adequate tread remaining and the brakes are in serviceable condition. This is a solid, dependable vehicle for a buyer looking for everyday transportation without the premium price of a near-mint car. Buyers should expect a car that looks and drives well but carries the honest marks of prior use.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition at $47,500, and every dollar of that price is justified by what you'll find. The exterior is stunning \u2014 the paint is deep, vibrant, and mirror-like with absolutely no scratches, chips, fading, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, the trim is pristine, and the glass is crystal clear without a single crack or chip. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells virtually new \u2014 the seats show no wear, the carpets are spotless, and every surface is free of scuffs or staining. All electronics, controls, and features function exactly as intended with zero issues. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power. This is a vehicle that has been exceptionally cared for throughout its life, and it shows in every detail. A buyer can expect to drive this car with full confidence and minimal near-term maintenance concerns.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Searching for a vehicle that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You've found it! This stunning car is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 flawless inside and out, with every system running perfectly and zero compromises to be found. The interior is spotless, the exterior gleams without a blemish, and everything works exactly as it should. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly exceptional vehicle that has been kept in outstanding shape \u2014 don't let it pass you by!",
